data.description: This luxurious house boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, making it a perfect haven for a family or those who appreciate extra space and comfort. As you approach the house, you'll be impressed by its beautiful exterior and 3 car garage, which offers ample parking space and room for storage. Upon entering the house, you are greeted by a grand foyer that leads you into the heart of the home. The open-concept living area is spacious and has large windows that allow natural light to flood in. The kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with stainless steel appliances, stone countertops making it a central hub for family gatherings and entertaining. The family room, conveniently located near the kitchen, opens up to a patio with a beautiful view of the backyard. Step outside, and you'll find a stunning saltwater pool, perfect for cooling off on hot summer days or simply lounging by the water. The backyard also features a well-landscaped garden and outdoor seating areas, making it an ideal spot for relaxation and outdoor entertaining. The house includes a bonus room that can serve as a home office, playroom or even a home theater, depending on your preferences. With its flexibility, this space adds an extra layer of functionality to the property. The primary bedroom suite includes a walk-in closet and a luxurious en suite bathroom with a soaking tub, dual sinks and a separate shower. The other 2 bathrooms in the house are well-designed and modern, offering convenience and comfort for the entire family and guests. Whether you're enjoying the stylish interior, hosting gatherings in the backyard, or relaxing by the pool, this house is designed to meet the needs of those who appreciate the finer things in life. Come see for yourself! SELLERS WILL CREDIT THE BUYER(S) UP TO $15,000.00 TOWARDS A NEW ROOF AT CLOSING.
